Skirmish
		Map
      each player can place 4 enviroment pieces for a total of 10 eco points.
      each player can relocate 2 enviroment pieces.

		Objectives
      First player to reach a point goal, or defeat all enemy slimes wins. 
      To score points players must defeat enemy slimes. In this game mode large slimes are 2 points and small slimes are 1 point.
      -First to 5 points is the standard

    Deck building
      Decks are 40 cards with a maximum of 3 copys of any card
      
